      • index

        public static <E> int[] index​(XGettingSequence<E> sequence,
                              Predicate<? super E> predicate)
        Creates an array containing the indices of all elements the passed predicate applies to.
        Type Parameters:
        E - the element type of the passed sequence.
        Parameters:
        sequence - the sequence to be indexed.
        predicate - the predicate to be used to create the index.
        Returns:
        the index describing the passed predicate for the passed sequence.
